Research (ISPOR). Published by Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.jval.2016.02.017
PMCID: PMC5193154
PMID: 27987642 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


420. Value Health. 2016 Dec;19(8):936-944. doi: 10.1016/j.jval.2016.05.015. Epub
