The anti-tumor effects of the recombinant toxin protein rLj-RGD3 from Lampetra 
japonica on pancreatic carcinoma Panc-1 cells in nude mice.

Wang Y(1), Zheng Y(2), Tu Z(1), Dai Y(1), Xu H(1), Lv L(3), Wang J(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pharmacology, Dalian Medical University, Dalian, Liaoning 
Province 116044, China.
(2)School of Life Sciences, Liaoning Normal University, Dalian, Liaoning 
Province 116029, China.
(3)Department of Pharmacology, Dalian Medical University, Dalian, Liaoning 
